{"type":"message","timestamp":"2026-06-15T15:47:21.980Z","role":"assistant","content":" stable and viable strategy. A VGG-11 model with SSA in the last layer achieved **83.09% accuracy** on CIFAR","delta":true}
{"type":"message","timestamp":"2026-06-15T15:47:22.232Z","role":"assistant","content":"-10, compared to **86.46%** for the standard ReLU baseline.\n4.  **Capacity Bottleneck**: Competitive","delta":true}
